    - key: tutorial_lose_condition
      translations:
      - "<color=#446890>WHEN YOU</color> <color=#FF6567>\nHIT YOURSELF</color>\n<color=#446890>YOU WILL LOSE!</color> "
      - "<color=#446890>QUAND TU</color> <color=#FF6567>\nTE PERCUTES</color>\n<color=#446890>TU PERDRAS !</color>"
      - "<color=#446890>自分に</color><color=#FF6567>\nぶつかると</color>\n<color=#446890>ゲームオーバー！</color>"
      - "<color=#446890>자신에게</color><color=#FF6567>\n부딪히면</color>\n<color=#446890>게임 오버!</color>"
      - "<color=#446890>JIKA KAU</color><color=#FF6567>\nMENABRAK DIRI SENDIRI</color>\n<color=#446890>KAMU KALAH!</color>"
      - "<color=#446890>WENN DU</color><color=#FF6567>\nDICH SELBST TRIFFST</color>\n<color=#446890>VERLIERST DU!</color>"
      - "<color=#446890>SI TE</color> <color=#FF6567>\nCHOCAS CONTIGO</color>\n<color=#446890>¡PERDERÁS!</color>"
      - "<color=#446890>SE TI</color><color=#FF6567>\nCOLPISCI</color>\n<color=#446890>PERDI!</color>"
      - "<color=#446890>SE VOCÊ</color><color=#FF6567>\nBATER EM SI MESMO</color>\n<color=#446890>VOCÊ PERDE!</color>"
      - "<color=#446890>ЕСЛИ ТЫ</color><color=#FF6567>\nВРЕЖЕШЬСЯ В СЕБЯ</color>\n<color=#446890>ТЫ ПРОИГРАЕШЬ!</color>"
      - "<color=#446890>KENDİNE</color><color=#FF6567>\nÇARPARSAN</color>\n<color=#446890>KAYBEDERSİN!</color>"
    - key: tutorial_combo
      translations:
      - "\"<color=#446890>COMPLETE</color> <color=#FF6567>\nMULTIPLE ORDERS AT ONE VISIT</color>\n<color=#446890>AND EARN COINS</color> \""
      - "<color=#446890>COMPLÈTE</color> <color=#FF6567>\nPLUSIEURS COMMANDES EN UNE VISITE</color>\n<color=#446890>ET GAGNE DES PIÈCES</color>"
      - "<color=#446890>1回で</color><color=#FF6567>\n複数の注文を完了</color>\n<color=#446890>してコインを獲得</color>"
      - "<color=#446890>한 번에</color><color=#FF6567>\n여러 주문 완료하고</color>\n<color=#446890>코인 획득</color>"
      - "<color=#446890>SELESAIKAN</color><color=#FF6567>\nBEBERAPA PESANAN DALAM SATU KUNJUNGAN</color>\n<color=#446890>DAN DAPATKAN KOIN</color>"
      - "<color=#446890>SCHLIESSE</color><color=#FF6567>\nMEHRERE BESTELLUNGEN IN\\nEINEM BESUCH AB</color>\n<color=#446890>UND VERDIENE MÜNZEN</color>"
      - "<color=#446890>COMPLETA</color><color=#FF6567>\nVARIOS PEDIDOS EN UNA VISITA</color>\n<color=#446890>Y GANA MONEDAS</color>"
      - "<color=#446890>COMPLETA</color><color=#FF6567>\nPIÙ ORDINI IN UNA VISITA</color>\n<color=#446890>E GUADAGNA MONETE</color>"
      - "<color=#446890>COMPLETE</color><color=#FF6567>\nVÁRIOS PEDIDOS EM UMA VISITA</color>\n<color=#446890>E GANHE MOEDAS</color>"
      - "<color=#446890>ВЫПОЛНЯЙ</color><color=#FF6567>\nНЕСКОЛЬКО ЗАКАЗОВ ЗА ВИЗИТ</color>\n<color=#446890>И ЗАРАБАТЫВАЙ МОНЕТЫ</color>"
      - "<color=#446890>BİR ZİYARETTE</color><color=#FF6567>\nBİRDEN FAZLA SİPARİŞİ TAMAMLA</color>\n<color=#446890>VE PARA KAZAN</color>"
    - key: core_streak_intro_body
      translations:
      - Win <color=#8929F6>{0}</color> levels to activate <color=#8929F6>D.A.S.H. Boost</color> !
      - Gagne <color=#8929F6>{0}</color> niveaux pour activer <color=#8929F6>D.A.S.H. Élan</color> !
      - '<color=#8929F6>{0}</color>レベル勝利で<color=#8929F6>D.A.S.H. ブースト</color>を発動!'
      - '<color=#8929F6>{0}</color>레벨 클리어로 <color=#8929F6>D.A.S.H. 부스트</color> 활성화!'
      - Menangkan <color=#8929F6>{0}</color> level untuk mengaktifkan <color=#8929F6>D.A.S.H. Dorongan</color>!
      - Gewinne <color=#8929F6>{0}</color> Level, um <color=#8929F6>D.A.S.H. Schub</color> zu aktivieren!
      - Gana <color=#8929F6>{0}</color> niveles para activar <color=#8929F6>D.A.S.H. Impulso</color>!
      - Vinci <color=#8929F6>{0}</color> livelli per attivare <color=#8929F6>D.A.S.H. Potenziamento</color>!
      - Vença <color=#8929F6>{0}</color> níveis para ativar <color=#8929F6>D.A.S.H. Impulso</color>!
      - Выиграй <color=#8929F6>{0}</color> уровней чтобы активировать <color=#8929F6>D.A.S.H. Буст</color>!
      - '<color=#8929F6>{0}</color> seviye kazan ve <color=#8929F6>D.A.S.H. Gücü</color>''nü etkinleştir!'
